              "text": "ELDERLY MAN\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue_line_start",
              "children": [],
              "text": "When I was young, things were different."
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue_line_start",
              "children": [],
              "text": "We didn't have all these gadgets."
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue_line_start",
