              "text": "We talked to each other, face to face."
            }
          ],
          "text": "ELDERLY MAN\nWhen I was young, things were different.\nWe didn't have all these gadgets.\nWe talked to each other, face to face.\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue_block",
          "children": [
